    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>http://ntmscope.org/authors/admin/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://ntmscope.org/authors/admin/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This is the website of &lt;strong&gt;NTMscope&lt;/strong&gt;, a research project that investigates infections caused by non-tuberculous mycobacteria (NTM).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are based at the &lt;strong&gt;Mycobacterial Infection Research Unit (MIRU)&lt;/strong&gt; at University Hospital Frankfurt and the &lt;strong&gt;Research Center Borstel&lt;/strong&gt;, Germany.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We use a variety of epidemiological, clinical, microbiological and bioinformatic methods and aim primarily at elucidating the molecular epidemiology and resistance mechanisms in different NTM.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On this homepage, we share information regarding ongoing projects and provide access to the sequencing data generated in our studies. If you are willing to contribute to one of our studies, you are most welcome and can contact us via the form below.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
